                        <interp inst="t18480918-name-871" type="surname" value="HUGHES"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18480918-name-871" type="given" value="JOHN TIMOTHY"></interp>JOHN TIMOTHY HUGHES</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">policeman</hi>). The prisoner gave me his address—I went to his house, and found this coat on the bed.</p>
